abstract: >-
  DID:JIS implements the JTel Identity Standard for decentralized
  identifiers. Part of the HumoticaOS identity stack, it provides
  Ed25519-based identity management with DID Document creation,
  bilateral consent services, and TIBET provenance integration.
  Available as a 50KB Rust kernel with Python, JavaScript/WASM,
  and C bindings.
